description: Green Pirate is a liberating lifestyle company from Brooklyn NY, which aims to stimulate a hip and sexy culture of conscious healthy living in our community. From April through October, we offer fresh, healthy, delicious and nutritious refreshments from our renowned Community Juice Food Truck. This street level service allows us to reach across age, race, social, and political barriers in our community, making "health-food" accessible and affordable to all, and fostering an environment for growth.This is the new era of street food culture with fresh juice right on the curb!
name: Green Pirate
